OL,3,CGiving ex-Ofsted chief seat in Lords
OL,4,Cis an insult, says dead teacher's
OL,5,Csister
OL,7,FThe sister of a headteacher who took
OL,8,Fher own life after a school inspection
OL,9,Fhas branded reports that Ofsted's then-
OL,10,Fchief inspector could receive a seat
OL,11,Fin the House of Lords "an insult".
OL,13,FAmanda Spielman oversaw Ofsted when
OL,14,FRuth Perry died in 2023 after a report
OL,15,Fdowngraded her Caversham Primary
OL,16,FSchool in Reading, Berkshire, from its
OL,17,Fhighest rating to its lowest over
OL,18,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,26,@sD@WOUsD@aO]
