OL,3,CGiving ex-Ofsted chief seat in Lords
OL,4,Cis an insult, says dead teacher's
OL,5,Csister
OL,7,FAn inquest into the headteacher's
OL,8,Fdeath found the inspection had
OL,9,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,11,FAn independent review into how Ofsted
OL,12,Fhandled Mrs Perry's death found in
OL,13,F2024 it was "defensive and complacent".
OL,15,FMs Spielman, who served as the chief
OL,16,Finspector of the schools watchdog
OL,17,Fbetween 2017 and 2023, is reported to
OL,18,Fhave been nominated for a peerage by
OL,19,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch.
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@fO]
