OL,3,CGiving ex-Ofsted chief seat in Lords
OL,4,Cis an insult, says dead teacher's
OL,5,Csister
OL,7,FProfessor Julia Waters, Mrs Perry's
OL,8,Fsister, said Ms Spielman's "legacy is
OL,9,Findelibly associated with my sister's
OL,10,Fterrible, preventable death and with
OL,11,Fdefending the inhumane system that led
OL,12,Fto her death".
OL,14,FProf Waters added: "Through her
OL,15,Fresponse to Ruth's death and the
OL,16,Fsubsequent inquest and inquiries while
OL,17,Fhead of Ofsted, Amanda Spielman showed
OL,18,Fherself to be lacking in many of the
OL,19,Fqualities that you would hope would be
OL,20,Fneeded in Parliament.
OL,26,@pD@\OUtD@MO]vD@TOU
