OL,3,CGiving ex-Ofsted chief seat in Lords
OL,4,Cis an insult, says dead teacher's
OL,5,Csister
OL,7,F"She showed poor leadership and
OL,8,Fjudgement, a lack of empathy and
OL,9,Funderstanding of the issues, and a
OL,10,Ftendency to deflect any criticism onto
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,F"A record like that should not be
OL,14,Frewarded with a place in the House of
OL,15,FLords. Spielman's nomination for a
OL,16,Fpeerage is a disgrace and an insult to
OL,17,Fmy sister's memory."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@TO]
