OL,3,CGiving ex-Ofsted chief seat in Lords
OL,4,Cis an insult, says dead teacher's
OL,5,Csister
OL,7,FEarlier this month, Ms Spielman
OL,8,Fpublicly criticised Education
OL,9,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson, and the
OL,10,FChildren's Wellbeing and Schools Bill.
OL,12,FThe former Ofsted chief said the Bill
OL,13,Fwas likely to make education in
OL,14,FEngland worse, and accused Ms
OL,15,FPhillipson of being "influenced" by
OL,16,Fthe schools unions.
