OL,7,FMs Spielman was rebuked by a
OL,8,FGovernment source, who claimed she
OL,9,Fshould "spend less time criticising
OL,10,Fthe reforms this Government is
OL,11,Fbringing, and more time reflecting on
OL,12,Fher failure at Ofsted".
OL,14,FA Conservative party spokesman would
OL,15,Fnot comment on reports of Ms
OL,16,FSpielman's nomination for a peerage.
